Hey There
/$
$
The Purple Lotus Kava Bars have been a leading Kava institution in South Florida for over 18 years, setting the standard. We strive to relax and chill out our patrons with ancient drinks created to relieve anxiety and stress.
We are the original West Palm Beach, Delray Beach and South Beach Kava Bars...  And damn proud of it.
/$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
All About Kava
/$
$
Kava is both a plant, and a beverage produced from the root of the same plant.  At the Purple Lotus, we offer both forms: a powdered kava root and a kava beverage.  Either way, you're going to get a product prepared with love.
​
Traditionally, kava is consumed for its sedative and anti-anxiety qualities - helping to relax without disrupting mental clarity.  The plant itself is a tall-growing shrub in the pepper family that thrives in the South Pacific. Vanuatu is the leading producer of kava, sometimes being referred to as the "home" of kava - you should try our Vanuatu Kava sometime...
